2018-05-?? 1.2
  - Support for custom defaults and special profiles in
    $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/torf/config
  - New options: --config/-F, --profile/-f, --noexclude/-E, --nomagnet/-M


2018-04-08 1.1
  - Major rewrite with lots of tests that should fix the most obvious bugs
  - The options --source and --nosource have been removed
  - The option --nocreator has been added
  - Output is now easier to parse when stdout is not a TTY (e.g. when piping to
    grep, cut, awk, etc)


2018-02-01 1.0
  Final release


2018-01-15 1.0a1
  Initial release
